 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-207">A pesquisa é executada em objetos que são identificados pelo nome diferenciado especificado no atributo do objeto base.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-207">The search is performed against the objects that are identified by the distinguished name that is specified in the attribute of the base object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-208">Por exemplo, se o objeto base é uma classe de grupo de adschema e o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> é definido como "member", em seguida, a pesquisa será executada em todos os objetos que são membros do grupo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-208">For example, if the base object is an adschema group class and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> is set to "member," then the search will be performed against all objects that are members of the group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-209">Para obter mais informações, consulte o tópico da classe adschema "Grupo" na biblioteca MSDN em [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-209">For more information, see the adschema "Group" class topic in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-210">Quando o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> propriedade for usada, o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> propriedade deve ser definida como <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-210">When the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property is used, the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property must be set to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-211">Se o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> estiver definida como qualquer outro valor, definindo o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> propriedade lançará um <xref:System.ArgumentException>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-211">If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property is set to any other value, setting the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property will throw an <xref:System.ArgumentException>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-212">Para obter mais informações, consulte o tópico "Executando uma consulta de escopo de atributo" na biblioteca MSDN em [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library)).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-212">For more information, see the "Performing an Attribute Scope Query" topic in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library)).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-213">O exemplo a seguir mostra como usar o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> propriedade com o atributo de membro para obter os membros de um grupo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-213">The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property with the member attribute to get the members of a group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-214">Em seguida, imprime os nomes e sobrenomes dos membros e seus números de telefone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-214">It then prints out the first and last names of the members and their telephone numbers.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
DirectoryEntry group = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=MyGroup, …");  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher(group "(&(objectClass=user)(objectCategory=Person))");  
src.AttributeScopedQuery = "member";  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("sn");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("givenName");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("telephoneNumber");  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll())  
{  
    Console.WriteLine("…");  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-232">O exemplo c# a seguir mostra como definir a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> propriedade para <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> , de modo que ele desreferencia os aliases ao pesquisar subordinados e localizar objetos de base.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-232">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> property to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> , so that it dereferences aliases when both searching subordinates and locating base objects.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
// Set DerefAlias to Always.  
src.DerefAlias = DerefenceAlias.Always;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-242">O exemplo a seguir mostra como retornar uma coleção de nomes distintos em formato hexadecimal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-242">The following example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-303">Se <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> é uma referência nula (`Nothing` no Visual Basic), a raiz de pesquisa é definida como a raiz do domínio que o servidor está usando no momento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-303">If <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), the search root is set to the root of the domain that your server is currently using.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-304">Há várias maneiras para pesquisar no catálogo global:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-304">There are several ways to search in the global catalog:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-305">Enumerar o catálogo global e escolha o primeiro filho.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-305">Enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-306">Especifique o nome do servidor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-306">Specify the server name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-307">Use a função DsGetDcName para encontrar o catálogo global.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-307">Use the DsGetDcName function to find the global catalog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-308">Para obter mais informações sobre a função DsGetDcName, veja o tópico "DsGetDcName" na biblioteca MSDN em [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-308">For more information on the DsGetDcName function, see the topic "DsGetDcName" in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-309">Obter RootDSE do catálogo global e solicite "rootNamingContext".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-309">Get the RootDSE  of the global catalog and ask for "rootNamingContext".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-310">Use o catálogo global, especificando um caminho de pesquisa, como se usando o LDAP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-310">Use the global catalog, specifying a search path as if using LDAP.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-311">Por exemplo, "GC: / / UO =..., DC =..., DC =...".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-311">For example, "GC://OU=..., DC=..., DC=...".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-312">O código c# a seguir mostra como enumerar o catálogo global e escolha o primeiro filho.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-312">The following C# code shows how to enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
    ```csharp  
    DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("GC://forestname");  
    IEnumerator ie = entry.Children.GetEnumerator();  
    ie.MoveNext();  
    entry = (DirectoryEntry)ie.Current;  
    DirectorySearcher search = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
    ```

  
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.SecurityMasks = SecurityMasks.Dacl | SecurityMasks.Owner;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3f6e5-350">O exemplo c# a seguir mostra como definir a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> propriedade para `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3f6e5-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("(isDeleted=true)");  
//Set the Tombstone property to true.  
